a message, will you?


73
00:07:06.730 --> 00:07:07.992
Tell him that
we're all ready here.


74
00:07:08.906 --> 00:07:11.386
We-
- Yes. We're ready to go.

75
00:07:12.736 --> 00:07:14.781
Yes, it's Raymond Beaty again.

76
00:07:14.825 --> 00:07:15.608
Yes, he--

77
00:07:16.783 --> 00:07:17.436
Hello?

78
