86
00:07:50.164 --> 00:07:51.209
Hey, look at me.

87
00:07:57.694 --> 00:07:58.346
Will we be all right?

88
00:08:00.131 --> 00:08:00.653
I don't know.

89
00:08:02.481 --> 00:08:03.264
Come here.

90
00:08:04.614 --> 00:08:05.397
There you go.

91
00:08:07.181 --> 00:08:08.226
Beautiful.

92
00:08:16.713 --> 00:08:17.365
Ray?

93
00:08:22.153 --> 00:08:22.936
I'm scared.

94
00:08:24.851 --> 00:08:26.026
It's okay.

95
00:08:26.766 --> 00:08:27.332
We all are.

96
00:08:30.770 --> 00:08:32.859
[Clara] Even Dad? Yeah.

97
00:08:34.382 --> 00:08:35.427
Even Dad.

98
00:08:55.229 --> 00:08:57.754
Did you know that the sun's rays
take eight minutes to reach here?


99
00:08:59.103 --> 00:08:59.756
Earth.

100
00:09:02.236 --> 00:09:03.324
I read that somewhere.

101
00:09:03.890 --> 00:09:05.849
[laughs]

102
00:09:07.764 --> 00:09:09.461
You remind me so much
of your mother sometimes.


103
00:09:11.593 --> 00:09:12.638
