104
00:09:16.686 --> 00:09:17.469
I need you, Raymond.

105
00:09:20.124 --> 00:09:21.342
I need you to grow up.

106
00:09:22.387 --> 00:09:23.649
If we're gonna survive this,

107
00:09:25.172 --> 00:09:27.522
your brother and I need you to
be the man I know you can be.


108
00:09:29.786 --> 00:09:31.962
I think we need to think a
little bit more realistically


109
00:09:32.005 --> 00:09:33.093
about what's going
on here, Dad.


110
00:09:35.095 --> 00:09:35.879
About what's happening.

111
00:09:36.923 --> 00:09:38.011
About these caves.

112
00:09:43.756 --> 00:09:45.323
Find your mother.
It's almost dinner time.


113
00:10:04.821 --> 00:10:05.735
[sighs]

114
00:10:10.043 --> 00:10:11.523
[lamp buzzing]

115
00:10:29.106 --> 00:10:30.411
[gasps]

116
00:10:31.369 --> 00:10:32.413
[chuckles]

117
00:10:34.328 --> 00:10:35.373
Sorry.

118
00:10:40.334 --> 00:10:41.640
I made pot pie for dinner.

119
00:10:42.772 --> 00:10:43.773
You still like pot pie,
don't you?


120
00:10:44.948 --> 00:10:45.818
Um...

121
00:10:47.864 --> 00:10:48.647
