123
00:10:51.693 --> 00:10:53.391
Yeah, uh, Fred just showed up.
He's here.


124
00:10:54.914 --> 00:10:55.741
He brought someone.

125
00:11:00.398 --> 00:11:02.617
[softly] One, two, three,
four, five, six, seven...


126
00:11:02.922 --> 00:11:04.315
[classical piano music playing]

127
00:11:04.750 --> 00:11:05.577
Oh.

128
00:11:07.535 --> 00:11:09.363
She's been moving
a lot lately.[chuckles]


129
00:11:09.886 --> 00:11:10.712
Oh, wow, so it's a girl?

130
00:11:12.236 --> 00:11:13.019
Do you have a name?

131
00:11:13.585 --> 00:11:14.194
Claudine.

132
